SUMMARY:Kinkaku-ji (Golden Pavilion) (金閣寺)
LOCATION:金閣寺\, Kinkaku-ji (Golden Pavilion)
DESCRIPTION:京都最著名嘅金色寺廟\,庭園平坦易行\\nTip: 早上陽光最靚\,寺內有休息座位。搭巴士101或205號直達\,步行距離短\\nGoogle: 4.5⭐\\nDuration: 1小時\\nMaps: https://www.google.com/maps/search/Kinkaku-ji%20(Golden%20Pavilion)%20%E4%BA%AC%E9%83%BD%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA
